@node what_is_this "What is Mr Icon?"

             (Ÿ`Ṗ._.Ṗ' Mr Icon `Ṗ._.Ṗ'Ÿ)


         (_.Ṗ'Ÿ`Ṗ What is Mr Icon? Ṗ'Ÿ`Ṗ._)


 A few years ago I got annoyed over that there was
 no program for simply copying an icon image and for
 giving an icon to objects who didn't have one!!!


 When you're simply in need of copying an
 icon, or create a default icon for an object there
 was a problem - no such program existed!

 So I made a drag n' drop-able GUI for copying
 icons.

 This was the first program I localized. :)


 As simple as that :)

@endnode
